1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,937
=Episode 18=

3
00:00:17,487 --> 00:00:18,126
Father!

4
00:00:22,519 --> 00:00:23,160
Father!

5
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:30,239
Father!

6
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:33,960
Chang.

7
00:00:34,840 --> 00:00:37,640
That Thousand-year Lingzhi
has remarkable properties.

8
00:00:38,159 --> 00:00:38,880
And since

9
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:41,039
your internal energy is so abundant,

10
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:42,759
one dose is all you need

11
00:00:44,100 --> 00:00:45,119
to make a full recovery.

12
00:00:45,799 --> 00:00:46,439
Father...

13
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:49,280
I never understood

14
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:52,359
why you left so abruptly back then.

15
00:00:57,439 --> 00:00:59,880
Was there some secret
you couldn't share?

16
00:01:06,359 --> 00:01:07,680
I left without a word

17
00:01:09,519 --> 00:01:11,200
so I wouldn't implicate
you and your aunt.

18
00:01:13,690 --> 00:01:14,799
You failed in your mission?

19
00:01:15,319 --> 00:01:16,680
I managed to escape unharmed.

20
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,560
Then, where have you been

21
00:01:21,799 --> 00:01:22,959
all these years?

22
00:01:26,439 --> 00:01:27,200
Chang,

23
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:31,280
the world might call our family

24
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:32,920
Martial Arts Titans,

25
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:35,519
but to the Imperial Court,

26
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:38,680
we are a threat to their stability.

27
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:40,439
Especially since

28
00:01:41,799 --> 00:01:43,599
we lost a gift bestowed by the Emperor.

29
00:01:45,319 --> 00:01:49,200
I spent these years
searching for the Sacred Token

30
00:01:50,599 --> 00:01:52,040
so I wouldn't cause you more trouble.

31
00:01:53,610 --> 00:01:55,040
I never imagined that after I left,

32
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,879
your grandfather
would train you to take my place.

33
00:01:58,319 --> 00:01:59,519
Your aunt, however...

34
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,640
She was always too rigid.

35
00:02:02,319 --> 00:02:04,079
In the end, she let this massive burden

36
00:02:04,959 --> 00:02:06,319
fall squarely on your shoulders.

37
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:09,439
Chang,

38
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,800
it was shortsighted of me.

39
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:15,319
It was my mistake.

40
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:17,599
Father.

41
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,560
Once we recover the Sacred Token,

42
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,400
could our family

43
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,759
retire from the Martial World?

44
00:02:22,537 --> 00:02:25,319
Then, Buyu and I could finally marry.

45
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,800
The two of us will surely
take good care of you,

46
00:02:28,162 --> 00:02:29,803
and Auntie and Uncle as well.

47
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:32,800
Very well.

48
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,400
I shall look forward to that day.

49
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,879
I'll pretend to check in.

50
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:48,380
The secret guards will lie in ambush.

51
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,120
Wait for my signal arrow.

52
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,400
Do not move until then.

53
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,350
- Understood!
- Understood!

54
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:01,639
Father...

55
00:03:01,879 --> 00:03:03,759
While you were traveling
the Martial World,

56
00:03:04,660 --> 00:03:06,759
did you pick up any news
regarding the Sacred Token?

57
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,240
During those years,

58
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,759
I joined a secret order.

59
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:17,439
I cannot reveal their identity to you,

60
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:19,599
but with their assistance,

61
00:03:20,420 --> 00:03:22,280
I tracked down
the Sacred Token's whereabouts.

62
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:25,000
The man who stole
the silver "left-hand" token

63
00:03:26,187 --> 00:03:28,548
from that scoundrel
Dongfang Qing recently

64
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:30,879
was me.

65
00:03:32,879 --> 00:03:34,599
That explains why he was so certain

66
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,439
that our sect had stolen it.

67
00:03:36,879 --> 00:03:38,840
The token Dongfang Qing possessed

68
00:03:39,759 --> 00:03:41,400
was only the silver "left-hand" piece.

69
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:44,000
As for the solid gold Sacred Token

70
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:46,479
is still missing.

71
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:49,280
So he never had

72
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,280
both pieces of the Sacred Token?

73
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:53,680
Then...

74
00:03:54,550 --> 00:03:56,319
Are the other three
Thief Kings still alive?

75
00:03:56,639 --> 00:03:57,240
No.

76
00:03:58,479 --> 00:03:59,560
I have investigated.

77
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:01,240
Aside from Dongfang Qing,

78
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:03,719
the other three are certainly dead.

79
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,240
So there really is
a mastermind behind him.

80
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,190
I should've been more careful.

81
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,879
If I had spared Dongfang Qing's life,

82
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:14,520
we might have found a lead

83
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,279
on the other Sacred Token.

84
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,959
Do not blame yourself, Chang.

85
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:21,680
That old devil brought it upon himself
by trying to trap you.

86
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,879
(Why does he have
an Embroidered Guard badge?)

87
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:59,399
(Is it stolen, or is he...)

88
00:05:00,519 --> 00:05:01,600
(Who is he exactly?)

89
00:05:02,825 --> 00:05:05,319
(Tangshan Hot Spring Inn)

90
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,000
Sir...

91
00:05:09,079 --> 00:05:09,920
Sir!

92
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:11,759
You can't just barge in.

93
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:13,199
We have a business to run!

94
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,639
Wushuang.

95
00:05:17,319 --> 00:05:18,000
Rong?

96
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,680
Wushuang,

97
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,240
why have you brought a troop
to Tangshan?

98
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,920
Rong, where is Buyu?

99
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,160
Buyu is in the backyard.

100
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,560
Is Chu Yunchang here as well?

101
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,240
Yes, she is.

102
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,240
Attendant!

103
00:05:35,399 --> 00:05:36,959
Prepare some fodder for my horse.

104
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:37,720
Certainly, sir.

105
00:05:39,330 --> 00:05:41,240
Once we're inside,
keep a sharp eye on everyone.

106
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:42,600
Let no one escape.

107
00:05:59,120 --> 00:05:59,759
Buyu.

108
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,040
What are you doing?

109
00:06:02,439 --> 00:06:03,160
Squire Mei?

110
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,639
What brings you here?

111
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,839
I was looking for my distant...

112
00:06:08,300 --> 00:06:09,199
I was coming here to...

113
00:06:09,199 --> 00:06:09,839
Buyu!

114
00:06:10,759 --> 00:06:12,240
I've been looking all over for you.

115
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,040
Squire Mei.

116
00:06:14,639 --> 00:06:15,240
Xu.

117
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:16,959
Wushuang is here.

118
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,079
What is she doing here?

119
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:29,600
Chang.

120
00:06:31,437 --> 00:06:32,038
(Sacred Token)
Keep this safe.

121
00:06:33,587 --> 00:06:34,188
This...

122
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,600
Make sure it's safe.

123
00:06:38,300 --> 00:06:40,312
(Sacred Token)

124
00:06:46,959 --> 00:06:47,560
Father.

125
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:49,399
I'm heading back to the inn.

126
00:06:52,279 --> 00:06:53,439
Wushuang, why are you here?

127
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:55,160
I'm here...

128
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,759
I'm here for the hot springs.

129
00:07:01,879 --> 00:07:02,680
Come again?

130
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,160
For leisure and amusement.

131
00:07:06,730 --> 00:07:08,160
If you all are allowed to have fun,

132
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,279
can't I come to relax as well?

133
00:07:10,279 --> 00:07:11,519
Yeah, right.

134
00:07:11,879 --> 00:07:13,839
You brought a troop here
just for a soak?

135
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:14,480
What?

136
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:15,680
When you're in the spring,

137
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:18,040
do you need people
on the sidelines cheering you on?

138
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:19,059
But of course.

139
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:20,680
Why?

140
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:23,439
Do you have an issue with that?

141
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:25,439
There is no one else here.

142
00:07:26,439 --> 00:07:27,600
One more won't hurt anything.

143
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:28,600
- Actually, it will.
- Actually, it will.

144
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,319
We have a formal meeting as in-laws.

145
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,000
Tell me, Deputy Luo,

146
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:37,240
who exactly do you think
you are to interfere?

147
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,000
Meeting as in-laws?

148
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,639
You haven't had the ceremonies yet.

149
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,839
Besides, Uncle Mao isn't even here.

150
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,680
How is this a formal meeting?

151
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,920
All of you, head back.

152
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,839
Tell my grandfather

153
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:59,639
that I am perfectly safe here.

154
00:07:59,959 --> 00:08:00,639
(Wind, Flowers, Snow, and Moon)
Understood!

155
00:08:02,762 --> 00:08:03,560
Yu.

156
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:05,160
Are there vacant rooms here?

157
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,199
I'll go and check.

158
00:08:30,425 --> 00:08:32,025
Is this your only kitchen?

159
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,679
Yes, sir.

160
00:08:33,620 --> 00:08:34,480
What about the cook?

161
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,600
Squire Mei isn't fond
of outside cooking,

162
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,440
so their maid has taken over the meals.

163
00:08:42,312 --> 00:08:43,472
You may go now.

164
00:08:45,962 --> 00:08:46,962
Leave.

165
00:08:47,639 --> 00:08:48,200
Understood.

166
00:09:29,112 --> 00:09:30,352
(That girl is certainly lazy.)

167
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:31,890
(She didn't empty the slop bucket.)

168
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,600
She leaves the slop bucket full,

169
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:45,200
yet scrubs the medicine pot spotless.

170
00:09:54,279 --> 00:09:55,840
Actually, it's not that clean.

171
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:00,720
Chang.

172
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:05,720
Here.

173
00:10:12,812 --> 00:10:13,712
(Sacred Token)

174
00:10:15,625 --> 00:10:17,275
(Sacred Token)

175
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:17,960
This is...

176
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:20,480
Luo Wushuang is here to watch me.

177
00:10:20,799 --> 00:10:22,399
Keep this token with you for now.

178
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,360
We must stay on high alert

179
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,360
to deal with her.

180
00:10:25,879 --> 00:10:26,679
Yes, Sect Leader.

181
00:10:27,039 --> 00:10:27,919
I'll keep the token

182
00:10:28,039 --> 00:10:28,720
safe with me.

183
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:30,500
You must stay safe
even if the token isn't.

184
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:31,720
Understood.

185
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:34,440
This is bad! This is very bad!

186
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,159
Something big is going down!

187
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:38,960
What's wrong?

188
00:10:40,279 --> 00:10:41,039
What happened?

189
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,440
You were right!

190
00:10:42,679 --> 00:10:43,799
That female constable

191
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:45,279
did head straight for the kitchen.

192
00:10:45,279 --> 00:10:47,120
She's turning
the whole place upside down!

193
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,679
I knew it.

194
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:50,120
Once that Thousand-year Lingzhi
was bought,

195
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,690
Luo Wushuang was bound
to get suspicious.

196
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:54,919
But you have me, Zhizhi!

197
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:56,200
I already scrubbed

198
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,720
that kitchen spotless.

199
00:10:58,039 --> 00:10:59,720
She won't find a single trace.

200
00:11:00,039 --> 00:11:00,840
That's a relief.

201
00:11:01,559 --> 00:11:02,200
Chang,

202
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:04,720
you need to take your medicine quickly.

203
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,320
You must regain your strength

204
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,559
to deal with Luo Wushuang.

205
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,600
There's no need to rush.

206
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:19,279
Drink it slowly.

207
00:11:31,559 --> 00:11:32,320
Your Majesty.

208
00:11:32,559 --> 00:11:34,360
The silver Sacred Token has resurfaced.

209
00:11:35,562 --> 00:11:36,603
You've done well.

210
00:11:37,159 --> 00:11:38,679
Now, we only lack the right-hand token.

211
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,159
Are you saying...

212
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:45,639
Set aside all other concerns.

213
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,639
Focus entirely on finding that token.

214
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,399
Do you mean to say

215
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:52,360
the golden Sacred Token is in...

216
00:11:53,799 --> 00:11:54,679
Some things

217
00:11:55,559 --> 00:11:57,120
are best left unspoken.

218
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,120
May I ask Your Majesty,

219
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,360
is Chu Shan one of our own?

220
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:05,960
There are some things

221
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,080
that you are better off not knowing.

222
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:12,720
Understood.

223
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:17,960
Well?

224
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,639
Are you feeling any better?

225
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:23,480
This Thousand-year Lingzhi truly
has remarkable healing powers.

226
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,399
I've recovered most of my strength.

227
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:26,720
Ms. Chu?

228
00:12:29,525 --> 00:12:31,285
Ms. Chu, are you in there?

229
00:12:34,679 --> 00:12:36,159
It's her again.

230
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,600
What does she want now?

231
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:46,279
Ms. Chu?

232
00:12:46,399 --> 00:12:47,399
I'm coming in.

233
00:12:47,759 --> 00:12:48,600
I'm coming in now.

234
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:53,320
Deputy Luo,

235
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:55,360
is there something you need?

236
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:58,600
Let's head to the hot springs.

237
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,159
Just the two of us?

238
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,240
Rong will be there too.

239
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:10,720
But we aren't exactly
on such intimate terms.

240
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:15,200
Since we're out for leisure,

241
00:13:15,380 --> 00:13:16,960
we should enjoy ourselves to the fullest.

242
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:19,639
What? Are you afraid?

243
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:22,799
Or perhaps

244
00:13:23,399 --> 00:13:26,080
you simply have no wish
to join us, is that it?

245
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:34,279
As you surely know,

246
00:13:34,639 --> 00:13:37,120
I caught a severe chill
a couple of days ago.

247
00:13:37,799 --> 00:13:38,600
Is that so?

248
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:43,159
Then a soak is
what you need to drive out the cold.

249
00:13:44,879 --> 00:13:47,559
Or are you finding it difficult
to mention some other secret?

250
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:50,840
Not at all.

251
00:13:51,279 --> 00:13:53,320
You head over there first.

252
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:54,639
I will join you in a moment.

253
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,080
It's fine. I'll wait for you.

254
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,159
There's no rush.

255
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:00,480
(Chu Yunchang,)

256
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:03,399
(If I can just see
the injury on your back,)

257
00:14:04,159 --> 00:14:05,559
(I'll arrest you on the spot.)

258
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:08,039
(You want to see if I'm wounded?)

259
00:14:08,639 --> 00:14:09,799
(Keep dreaming.)

260
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:21,279
Come on, Ms. Chu!

261
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:25,559
Yunchang, Wushuang!

262
00:14:25,559 --> 00:14:27,039
Come on in, it feels wonderful!

263
00:14:27,559 --> 00:14:28,200
Very well.

264
00:14:34,919 --> 00:14:36,799
Why haven't you stripped down yet?

265
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:40,279
I...

266
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:46,080
It's fine if you're shy
about your figure.

267
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,519
We're all women here, after all.

268
00:14:47,759 --> 00:14:49,039
No one is going to judge you.

269
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,039
Or perhaps...

270
00:14:55,399 --> 00:14:57,240
is there something on your body that

271
00:14:57,519 --> 00:14:58,440
you're afraid we'll see?

272
00:14:58,650 --> 00:14:59,759
It's that time of the month.

273
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:02,600
What a coincidence.

274
00:15:03,679 --> 00:15:04,559
For you too?

275
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:05,320
I...

276
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:07,600
Yunchang, you shouldn't soak
if you're on your period.

277
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:08,799
Let me walk you back to rest.

278
00:15:08,879 --> 00:15:09,600
No need.

279
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,639
Stay and enjoy yourselves.

280
00:15:10,639 --> 00:15:11,639
I can manage on my own.

281
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:12,519
Ms. Chu,

282
00:15:12,799 --> 00:15:13,840
let me escort you.

283
00:15:13,860 --> 00:15:14,559
There's no need.

284
00:15:14,559 --> 00:15:15,519
I'll walk her back.

285
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:18,600
Ms. Chu!

286
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:19,960
Wait for me!

287
00:15:20,799 --> 00:15:21,879
When did Wushuang

288
00:15:22,279 --> 00:15:24,320
become so thoughtful toward others?

289
00:16:28,279 --> 00:16:29,519
Where could it be?

290
00:16:29,519 --> 00:16:30,000
Who's there?

291
00:16:35,462 --> 00:16:38,737
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

292
00:16:38,775 --> 00:16:41,650
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

293
00:16:42,150 --> 00:16:47,868
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

294
00:16:49,050 --> 00:16:52,370
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

295
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:55,420
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

296
00:16:56,588 --> 00:17:01,828
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

297
00:17:03,050 --> 00:17:05,443
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

298
00:17:05,443 --> 00:17:09,093
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

299
00:17:09,162 --> 00:17:12,652
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

300
00:17:12,750 --> 00:17:15,725
♪To the ends of time♪

301
00:17:15,725 --> 00:17:19,100
♪The moon traces your face♪

302
00:17:19,287 --> 00:17:22,875
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

303
00:17:22,875 --> 00:17:29,115
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

304
00:17:29,450 --> 00:17:32,665
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

305
00:17:32,950 --> 00:17:36,488
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

306
00:17:36,775 --> 00:17:39,800
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

307
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:42,900
♪On our way to forever♪

308
00:17:42,900 --> 00:17:46,750
♪The moon traces your face♪

309
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:50,110
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

310
00:17:50,300 --> 00:17:56,260
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

311
00:17:57,337 --> 00:18:06,977
♪Just to be with you♪
